snippet.title: Video: Fight at Petrol Pump over Rs 500 old Note in Saharanpur

localized.description:
Watch this CCTV footage video of Uttar Pradesh Petrol pump. Petrol pump worker and a customer scuffle over Rs 500 old note in Saharanpur. Petrol pump worker denied to accept banned currency note of 500 rupees.
